  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施组件之间的数据流图。起点是IngressController，它接收外部流量后转发给LoadBalancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，IngressController作为入口，然后直连LoadBalancer。接下来LoadBalancer会分发到后端吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，但这里有个细节——LoadBalancer需要先和EtcdCluster交互，获取服务发现配置，然后再做负载均衡决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在LoadBalancer后面加上了EtcdCluster。现在从Etcd出来应该回到另一个LoadBalancer做实际分发？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，但注意这是同一个LoadBalancer组件，只是逻辑上分为配置获取和实际转发两个阶段。为了避免混淆，我们用菱形表示决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，菱形表示这个LoadBalancer的决策逻辑。那决策之后分两条分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Yes分支走Redis缓存层。流量先到RedisCache，然后下发到WorkerNode处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Redis到WorkerNode，这是典型的缓存前置架构。WorkerNode处理完后数据流往哪走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "WorkerNode处理结果要回写另一个RedisCache，做结果缓存，然后这个RedisCache要把数据同步回IngressController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，结果缓存回到IngressController？通常Ingress是入口，这里变成出口回传了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "没错，这个IngressController同时承担响应回传的角色，属于双向流量。它收到结果后还需要更新EtcdCluster里的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，IngressController连到EtcdCluster。那Etcd更新完状态后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "EtcdCluster要连回那个菱形的LoadBalancer决策点，形成配置更新的闭环。这样下次请求就能拿到最新路由。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "闭环回到决策点，理解。那之前说的No分支呢？决策为No时走什么路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支是缓存未命中或异常路径，直接走另一个IngressController做降级处理，然后同样更新EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有两个IngressController？一个是主入口，一个是降级专用？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，虽然组件类型相同，但是不同实例。主IngressController在最前面，降级IngressController在No分支末端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。我检查一下：菱形LoadBalancer分出Yes到Redis-Worker-Redis-Ingress-Etcd-回菱形，No到另一个Ingress-Etcd结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "No分支的EtcdCluster后面好像断了？应该也要有个闭环，或者明确结束。让我再看一下——其实No分支的EtcdCluster到这里就可以了，不需要再连回去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，No分支是降级终止路径，EtcdCluster作为终点。不过我发现Yes分支最后Etcd连回菱形，但菱形之前已经出现过，这样画对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对的，这是故意设计的循环。每次请求都可能更新Etcd，然后立即影响下一次负载均衡决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解了，循环反馈机制。我调整一下布局，用ELK算法让循环结构更清晰。所有连线都是双向粗箭头表示强依赖？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，全部用粗等号线。再确认一遍组件：IngressController两个实例、LoadBalancer一个（菱形决策）、EtcdCluster两个连接点、RedisCache两个、WorkerNode一个。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部确认完毕。最终结构：起始于IngressController，经LoadBalancer到Etcd获取配置，决策后Yes分支走双层Redis加WorkerNode，回传经IngressController更新Etcd闭环；No分支走降级IngressController更新Etcd终止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
